  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety, tolerability and potential efficacy of
      IDH305 with standard treatments for newly diagnosed IDH1R132 mutant acute myeloid leukemia
      (AML).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
